        "Embarking on a concept of the Western Province Agricultural Services Authority Chairman, the first project of the opening of organic supermarkets and restaurants chain took place yesterday (22) under the distinguished patronage of the Western Province Governor and former Air Force Commander, Marshal of the Air Force Roshan Gunathilaka."
